h size effects are absent but plasticity avalanche\ndynamics is strongly universal, across sample width and aspect-ratio scales.\nFinally, we elucidate the mechanism that leads to the connection between\ndepinning and size effects in our model dislocation dynamics. In this way, our\nmodel builds a way towards unifying statistical aspects of mechanical\ndeformation across scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Nov 2015 20:42:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jun 2016 15:59:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-06"}
